 Sitecore Appoints Robert Calderoni to its Board of Directors 
         










    










 






 











 









Sitecore Appoints Robert Calderoni to its Board of Directors

		  Former Ariba CEO also serves on the board of directors for Citrix Systems, Juniper Networks and KLA-Tencor
		

Feb 25, 2015, 08:03 ET
		  		  						
						 from   Sitecore 











 
















































 

 















































 

 

 
 
 
 







Sitecore Logo.    
 Facebook
 Twitter
 Pinterest

































 




 




Sitecore Logo.
 


 

 




 





 


SAN FRANCISCO, Feb. 25, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- Sitecore, the global leader in customer experience management, today announced the appointment of Robert (Bob) M. Calderoni to its board of directors.  
"Bob brings to us a wealth of leadership, experience and proven capabilities in governing and managing competitive, fast-growing global businesses," said Michael Seifert, CEO and co-founder, Sitecore. "We are honored to have a new director of Bob's capabilities and skill serve on Sitecore's board." 
Calderoni has more than 30 years' experience in the technology industry as an executive and board member. He served as chairman and chief executive officer of Ariba for 13 years, and led the company through a period of rapid growth as it transformed from a traditional software company to one of the largest SaaS providers in the industry.  
Prior to his role as CEO at Ariba, Calderoni held senior executive positions at Apple and IBM. He has served as a chief financial officer at several large public companies.
Calderoni is also a member of the board of directors of Citrix Systems, Inc., Juniper Networks and KLA-Tencor, and currently serves as a senior advisor to SilverLake Partners. He holds a Bachelor of Science degree in public accounting & finance from Fordham University. 
About SitecoreSitecore is the global leader in customer experience management. The company delivers highly relevant content and personalized digital experiences that delight audiences, build loyalty and drive revenue. With the Sitecore® Experience Platform™, marketers can own the experience of every customer that engages with their brand, across every channel. More than 4,400 of the world's leading brands – including American Express, Carnival Cruise Lines, easyJet and L'Oréal trust Sitecore to help them deliver the meaningful interactions that win customers for life.
For more information, visit: www.sitecore.net.
ContactEmily Iwan Sitecore+1 (415) 326-7471pr@sitecore.net                                 
